  "title": "Talent Acquisition Coordinator",
  "description": "<p>Join RecruitFirst, where we connect amazing people with leading companies across industries! 🚀</p><p>📍 Location: Orchard</p><p>🕗 Working Schedule: Monday - Friday, 8:30am - 5:30pm</p><p>📆 Duration: Immediate - 3 months (extendable / convertible!)</p><p>💸 Salary: $12/h, incentives provided</p><p><u>Key responsibilities:</u></p><ul><li>Create attractive job advertisements that can attract top talent</li><li>Support mass hiring campaigns and special recruitment projects</li><li>Interview and shortlist candidates</li><li>Learn how to assess candidate fit and manage candidates expectations</li><li>Partner with clients to deliver great hiring results</li></ul><p><u>Who we are looking for:</u></p><ul><li>Fast learner who thrives in a dynamic, fast-paced environment</li><li>Detail-oriented, proactive, and confident communicator</li><li>Curious and eager to gain hands-on recruitment experience</li><li>Completed GCE A-Level / Diploma / Degree (any field)</li></ul>",
